  "detailed_description": "Upside Down will immerse you in an incredible adventure. Sharpen your reflexes for this fast-paced, precise puzzle-platformer. As a scarecrow armed only with your sharp wit, you will have to face deadly traps and dangerous wildlife to reach your goal. Each level is distinctive and exotic.<br />\r\nFigure out genuine puzzles and take the right path toward your salvation.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Unique levels<br />\r\n- Challenging puzzles<br />\r\n- Interesting obstacles and game mechanics<br />\r\n- Beautiful graphics and animations",
